{"tid":1874471,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"以為派口罩俾藍絲廢老就可以攏絡人心？知唔知咩叫八奇？","createTime":"2020-02-11T08:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T04:58:56.000Z","uid":20231,"like":233,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"26b5948d2bc4fa4bd4156c7266a778c5151aeaa5","tid":1874471,"uid":20231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuKoOzY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuKoOzY.jpg&h=6b871982&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffajmVb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffajmVb.jpg&h=39a48be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一味派糧根本就係最懶嘅做法，點樣將矛頭指向政府<br />\n我地要落井下石<br />\n藍絲有溫飽就屌黃絲，話知你邊個俾糧佢<br />\n要令佢屌政府，企我地一陣線，唔係一味派就得<br />\n<br />\n你仲要係黃絲都未必有口罩嘅情況救藍絲？<br />\n<br />\n叫口號係基本<br />\n口罩係派黃絲，入工會派口罩<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多方法，但絕對唔係鳩派"},{"pid":"0168a9790d8c78698a1ccde112bb0fb3ef2b438c","tid":1874471,"uid":20231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"荀彧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f8a836bc06f442998b026b393a375e8dd4a791","tid":1874471,"uid":20231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:24:45.000Z","msg":"你有能力就睇下啦"},{"pid":"577b8074d9ec2c7722f7c8546f4af15daaa3628d","tid":1874471,"uid":42942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"f85b9faec84f99b070f158e88b95cd84957ac6df","tid":1874471,"uid":251009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:33:26.000Z","msg":"火鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e9aa97ab0bccce7d1165bc095996090a72a886","tid":1874471,"uid":20231,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:33:31.00